Didn't you claim not to know how?

00:16:37.070 --> 00:16:37.840
[Cutie in Uniform]

00:16:37.840 --> 00:16:39.440
You're so cheeky, handsome.

00:16:41.390 --> 00:16:44.000
I'd love to see you in skirts.

