What kind of skirt do you like?

00:16:47.460 --> 00:16:47.790
[Rich Boy]

00:16:47.790 --> 00:16:50.440
Whatever kind you wear.

00:16:50.840 --> 00:16:51.960
A skirt like this?

00:17:00.600 --> 00:17:01.570
[The Trojan Horse is activated]

