[Real-time monitoring [Pinpointing]

00:17:03.510 --> 00:17:04.040
Found it.

00:17:05.109 --> 00:17:06.310
I found his location.

00:17:08.069 --> 00:17:09.640
Well done, Duozai!

00:17:39.920 --> 00:17:41.640
Great fun tonight, huh, Zhe?

00:17:42.110 --> 00:17:43.510
With those stamps, sure.

00:17:44.590 --> 00:17:45.720
Put it on the ground.

00:17:45.920 --> 00:17:46.580
Be careful.

00:17:46.790 --> 00:17:47.320
Careful.

00:17:50.200 --> 00:17:51.370
Xin,

00:17:51.440 --> 00:17:54.070
it already took us two trips,
yet there's still so much stuff.

00:17:54.070 --> 00:17:55.720
Put it down there. Stack it.

00:17:59.880 --> 00:18:00.750
Place this in its case.

00:18:00.750 --> 00:18:01.640
Okay.

00:18:01.640 --> 00:18:03.500
Be gentle. It's quite expensive.

00:18:07.920 --> 00:18:08.780
Be careful!

00:18:08.960 --> 00:18:10.200
Got it.

00:18:15.640 --> 00:18:17.400
Everyone, load the stuff
in the car outside!

00:18:17.400 --> 00:18:18.110
You don't need my help?

00:18:18.110 --> 00:18:18.680
No.

00:18:18.920 --> 00:18:19.960
Get that guitar out later!

00:18:19.960 --> 00:18:20.750
Got it!

00:18:23.540 --> 00:18:26.750
[A White Night]

00:18:28.400 --> 00:18:29.860
Don't turn off the lights.

00:18:30.480 --> 00:18:32.280
We haven't packed our stuff yet.

00:18:33.270 --> 00:18:34.040
Who are you?

00:18:41.590 --> 00:18:42.300
What now?

00:19:34.960 --> 00:19:35.890
Who's out there?

00:19:36.790 --> 00:19:37.880
Don't worry. It's one of us,

00:19:37.880 --> 00:19:38.590
Lin Qiong.

00:19:39.590 --> 00:19:41.990
You're pretty fast
at taking the cuffs off.

00:19:43.640 --> 00:19:44.900
Seriously, listen.

00:19:44.960 --> 00:19:46.200
You should take action

00:19:46.200 --> 00:19:47.860
with proper means from now on.

00:19:48.310 --> 00:19:49.550
What proper means?

00:19:50.270 --> 00:19:51.270
Getting a search warrant first

00:19:51.270 --> 00:19:52.830
and flashing my police badge?

00:19:52.830 --> 00:19:55.200
I've brought the suspects
and the drugs right to your face.

00:19:55.200 --> 00:19:56.200
I saved you so much trouble.

00:19:56.200 --> 00:19:57.270
Yet you're still yapping.

00:19:57.270 --> 00:19:59.080
I know you're smart and capable.

00:19:59.110 --> 00:20:01.340
You got into a fight,
so as to be arrested

00:20:01.400 --> 00:20:02.750
and to preserve your disguise.

00:20:02.750 --> 00:20:04.790
Then why are you still nagging,
now that you know my intentions?

00:20:04.790 --> 00:20:06.410
I'm just saying—

00:20:06.480 --> 00:20:08.400
couldn't you have gone easier on them?

00:20:08.400 --> 00:20:09.970
You should thank me.

00:20:10.270 --> 00:20:11.270
If I hadn't wrestled with them,

00:20:11.270 --> 00:20:13.510
you think those drugs
would've been flung out?

00:20:13.510 --> 00:20:14.240
What's more,

00:20:14.400 --> 00:20:16.110
I fought back
in order not to be beaten to death.

00:20:16.110 --> 00:20:17.480
I had to protect myself, right?

00:20:17.480 --> 00:20:18.520
Right. But you used

00:20:18.520 --> 00:20:20.070
excessive force in self-defense.

00:20:20.070 --> 00:20:20.880
How was it excessive?

00:20:20.880 --> 00:20:22.610
Those guys are in hospital now.

00:20:23.910 --> 00:20:25.880
They'll be able to talk tomorrow morning.

00:20:25.880 --> 00:20:26.720
It means we can't

00:20:26.720 --> 00:20:27.960
interrogate them now.

00:20:27.960 --> 00:20:29.780
Then do it tomorrow morning.

00:20:30.270 --> 00:20:32.600
Just focus on questioning Zhe.

00:20:32.790 --> 00:20:34.110
He knows the source of the drugs.

00:20:34.110 --> 00:20:34.550
Are you sure

00:20:34.550 --> 00:20:36.160
he truly knows the source?

00:20:36.560 --> 00:20:37.630
It depends on who will question him.

00:20:37.630 --> 00:20:39.830
If it's you, he might not tell the truth.

00:20:39.960 --> 00:20:41.310
You're unpleasantly blunt.

00:20:41.310 --> 00:20:42.200
So what then?

00:20:42.200 --> 00:20:43.110
Why don't you take my place

00:20:43.110 --> 00:20:44.640
and interrogate him instead?

00:20:44.640 --> 00:20:45.480
Fine by me.

00:20:46.070 --> 00:20:48.070
But do you have the final say on that?

00:20:48.200 --> 00:20:50.330
You win. I'd rather not argue with you.

00:20:50.640 --> 00:20:51.400
Why not I make a report to you

00:20:51.400 --> 00:20:52.110
before discussing further?

00:20:52.110 --> 00:20:52.790
Okay.

00:20:54.790 --> 00:20:56.970
Alright. After a thorough check,

00:20:57.070 --> 00:20:58.550
we found LSD stamps hidden

00:20:58.550 --> 00:21:00.270
in both the guitar and the vinyl.

00:21:00.270 --> 00:21:01.440
So, we can basically confirm

00:21:01.440 --> 00:21:03.960
that this is the way
they secretly transport goods.

00:21:03.960 --> 00:21:05.640
That makes things easy, right?

00:21:05.640 --> 00:21:07.790
Just investigate
the music store which sold that vinyl.

00:21:07.790 --> 00:21:09.050
I know that, of course.

00:21:09.070 --> 00:21:10.960
But there are many music stores
in Nanzhou.

00:21:10.960 --> 00:21:12.110
We're pressed for time.

00:21:12.110 --> 00:21:14.000
I need you to point out a new direction.

00:21:14.000 --> 00:21:16.200
Still, I think you should question Zhe.

00:21:16.400 --> 00:21:17.960
This complies with the rules.

00:21:17.960 --> 00:21:19.560
Isn't it what you care about?

00:21:19.960 --> 00:21:21.160
I shouldn't have bothered to ask you.

00:21:21.160 --> 00:21:21.960
Got any plans?

00:21:21.960 --> 00:21:23.290
I'm getting out of here.

00:21:23.440 --> 00:21:24.550
I just praised you for being smart.

00:21:24.550 --> 00:21:25.270
If you go out now,

00:21:25.270 --> 00:21:26.160
won't your cover be blown?

00:21:26.160 --> 00:21:27.290
You just had a fight.

00:21:27.750 --> 00:21:28.980
Take a good rest.

00:21:29.110 --> 00:21:29.550
Regain your composure.

00:21:29.550 --> 00:21:30.920
You can leave tomorrow morning.

00:21:30.920 --> 00:21:31.790
I'll have to stay overnight?

00:21:31.790 --> 00:21:32.280
Yes.

00:21:32.310 --> 00:21:32.720
By the way,

00:21:32.720 --> 00:21:34.180
what would you like to eat?

00:21:34.480 --> 00:21:35.880
Thread Noodle Porridge.

00:21:36.000 --> 00:21:36.790
Okay.

00:21:37.790 --> 00:21:38.640
Seriously, I have to stay overnight?

00:21:38.640 --> 00:21:39.700
You surely have to!

00:21:41.110 --> 00:21:41.970
Don't curse me.

00:21:56.920 --> 00:22:00.610
[Baiye Music Store]

00:22:08.820 --> 00:22:10.130
[Duozai]

00:22:11.550 --> 00:22:13.200
What did you find about Baiye Music Store?

00:22:13.200 --> 00:22:15.000
Between it and Tongle Formula Factory,

00:22:15.000 --> 00:22:15.990
there are deliveries.

00:22:15.990 --> 00:22:16.200
[Baiye Music Store]

00:22:16.200 --> 00:22:18.130
Goods are transported once a week.

00:22:18.440 --> 00:22:19.730
There's additional intel.

00:22:19.730 --> 00:22:20.920
I'll send it to you later.

00:22:20.920 --> 00:22:21.360
Okay.

00:22:22.000 --> 00:22:23.640
[Baiye Music Store]

00:22:27.960 --> 00:22:28.590
I think

00:22:28.680 --> 00:22:29.790
Duozai

00:22:29.960 --> 00:22:31.440
is quite efficient at work.

00:22:31.440 --> 00:22:33.040
He's a bit stubborn, though.

00:22:33.440 --> 00:22:34.510
With proper guidance,

00:22:34.510 --> 00:22:35.640
he'll achieve more.

00:22:39.440 --> 00:22:39.960
Didn't we already

00:22:39.960 --> 00:22:41.590
report the formula factory
to the police on the phone?

00:22:41.590 --> 00:22:43.520
Why are they still shipping goods?

00:22:44.440 --> 00:22:46.160
We only gave the police an anonymous tip

00:22:46.160 --> 00:22:47.560
without solid evidence.

00:22:48.110 --> 00:22:49.970
They wouldn't take it seriously.

00:22:59.960 --> 00:23:01.310
It seems we still need to

00:23:02.280 --> 00:23:03.790
start with Nanzhou.

00:23:05.790 --> 00:23:08.120
Only this is the main battleground for us.

00:23:09.940 --> 00:23:10.940
What do you think?

00:23:11.150 --> 00:23:12.410
Is it the type you want?

00:24:29.960 --> 00:24:30.820
Let me help you.

00:24:35.960 --> 00:24:37.160
When did you get here?

00:24:39.510 --> 00:24:40.510
A long time ago.

00:24:42.160 --> 00:24:43.420
Since you were asleep,

00:24:44.030 --> 00:24:45.160
I didn't wake you up.

00:25:07.960 --> 00:25:08.830
I'm sorry

00:25:10.410 --> 00:25:12.340
to have put you through suffering.

00:25:25.550 --> 00:25:26.370
Actually,

00:25:27.440 --> 00:25:29.040
he's fine in most of the time.

00:25:29.950 --> 00:25:31.440
But when he uses stamps,

00:25:32.430 --> 00:25:33.790
he'd act crazy

00:25:35.240 --> 00:25:36.480
and lose his mind.

00:25:48.390 --> 00:25:54.510
[A White Night]

00:25:57.750 --> 00:25:58.550
Take a look.

00:26:11.200 --> 00:26:12.930
I'll make him pay a steep price.

00:26:18.880 --> 00:26:21.080
I called the seller
to buy those stamps.

00:26:22.790 --> 00:26:25.050
That very number is no longer in service.

00:26:25.440 --> 00:26:26.550
Do you have any other way

00:26:26.550 --> 00:26:27.820
to contact the seller?

00:26:28.400 --> 00:26:28.920
No.

00:26:30.960 --> 00:26:32.490
Just that one phone number.

00:26:36.960 --> 00:26:39.160
How did you usually make transactions?

00:26:39.270 --> 00:26:41.120
He usually left the stamps

00:26:41.310 --> 00:26:42.440
at a designated spot

00:26:42.550 --> 00:26:43.480
for us to pick up.

00:26:45.110 --> 00:26:46.640
I bought one sheet at a time.

00:26:47.480 --> 00:26:50.140
He'd hide it in a vinyl
that would reach me later.

00:26:50.480 --> 00:26:52.740
Why were there stamps in the guitar then?

00:26:54.000 --> 00:26:55.640
When I ordered a large quantity,

00:26:55.640 --> 00:26:57.170
he'd put them in the guitar.

00:26:58.110 --> 00:27:00.770
I got that vinyl and the guitar
from him for free.

00:27:04.590 --> 00:27:06.650
When you ordered a large quantity...

00:27:07.640 --> 00:27:09.440
You bought a lot on a frequent basis.

00:27:09.440 --> 00:27:11.310
You couldn't have consumed
all the drugs yourself,

00:27:11.310 --> 00:27:11.920
right?

00:27:12.310 --> 00:27:14.110
Were you making money from them?

00:27:14.110 --> 00:27:16.110
You were obviously stocking drugs.

00:27:18.750 --> 00:27:19.550
Officer,

00:27:21.110 --> 00:27:22.440
I didn't own all of them.

00:27:23.640 --> 00:27:25.200
They were worth hundreds of thousands.

00:27:25.200 --> 00:27:27.140
I only did drugs for recreation

00:27:27.200 --> 00:27:27.960
and for fun.

00:27:28.480 --> 00:27:29.610
I dared not sell any.

00:27:31.480 --> 00:27:32.480
So you're saying

00:27:32.640 --> 00:27:33.570
you had partners

00:27:33.640 --> 00:27:35.040
in this business, right?

00:27:37.640 --> 00:27:38.900
Not exactly partners.

00:27:40.510 --> 00:27:41.110
I just...

00:27:41.920 --> 00:27:43.270
bought drugs for a guy.

00:27:43.960 --> 00:27:44.550
For whom?

00:27:47.640 --> 00:27:48.920
I'm asking who it was!

00:27:53.310 --> 00:27:53.880
Li Jun.

00:27:54.750 --> 00:27:55.810
How do you spell it?

00:27:56.920 --> 00:27:57.640
L-I, Li.

00:27:59.960 --> 00:28:01.020
J-U-N, Jun.

00:28:01.200 --> 00:28:02.110
Anyone else?

00:28:02.790 --> 00:28:03.920
A few of his friends.

00:28:06.960 --> 00:28:08.160
All the stamps in the guitar

00:28:08.160 --> 00:28:09.290
were ordered by him.

00:28:09.820 --> 00:28:13.340
♪ Good people lose and bad people win ♪

00:28:14.920 --> 00:28:20.640
♪ Life, oh, life ♪

00:28:20.640 --> 00:28:25.000
♪ The Highest Power
is watching everything we do ♪

00:28:28.960 --> 00:28:30.920
Come on, have drinks with us!

00:28:51.200 --> 00:28:52.800
A new product from my friend.

00:28:52.960 --> 00:28:53.620
Fancy a try?

00:29:08.960 --> 00:29:10.020
It's said to be able

00:29:10.440 --> 00:29:12.440
to make you feel like you're flying.

00:29:36.080 --> 00:29:38.770
[Everything about music]

00:29:38.770 --> 00:29:39.240
Hello, sir.

00:29:39.240 --> 00:29:40.240
How can I help you?

00:29:40.640 --> 00:29:42.200
My friend's guitar is broken.

00:29:42.200 --> 00:29:43.230
Have a look at it.

00:29:43.310 --> 00:29:44.070
This model...

00:29:44.070 --> 00:29:45.460
Do you know where I can buy one?

00:29:45.460 --> 00:29:46.410
This model?

00:29:46.830 --> 00:29:48.150
It's commonly seen.

00:29:48.400 --> 00:29:50.400
Many music stores sell such guitars.

00:29:50.400 --> 00:29:53.130
Which music store sells
second-hand vinyls now?

00:29:53.160 --> 00:29:54.590
Second-hand vinyls?

00:29:55.400 --> 00:29:56.590
Not many stores sell those.

00:29:56.590 --> 00:29:57.960
Those are usually seen in the stores

00:29:57.960 --> 00:29:59.200
owned by amateur musicians

00:29:59.200 --> 00:30:00.030
who enjoy collecting albums

00:30:00.030 --> 00:30:01.270
and musical instrument.

00:30:01.270 --> 00:30:03.330
Few places sell second-hand vinyls.

00:30:03.790 --> 00:30:05.270
Could you help me find out any store

00:30:05.270 --> 00:30:06.270
that sells those?

00:30:07.200 --> 00:30:08.550
I'll ask around for you.

00:30:08.550 --> 00:30:09.350
Thank you.

00:30:10.480 --> 00:30:11.180
Luo!

00:30:12.920 --> 00:30:13.790
We couldn't bring Li Jun back.

00:30:13.790 --> 00:30:14.410
Why?

00:30:14.790 --> 00:30:15.520
Last night,

00:30:15.550 --> 00:30:16.640
he accidentally fell off

00:30:16.640 --> 00:30:17.480
a hotel balcony

00:30:17.480 --> 00:30:18.160
and died.

00:30:18.310 --> 00:30:19.250
He fell and died?

00:30:19.790 --> 00:30:20.640
I got it.

00:30:20.640 --> 00:30:22.200
I'll call and ask Captain Lin about it.

00:30:22.200 --> 00:30:22.550
Okay.

00:30:24.310 --> 00:30:25.790
Do you know why Li Jun would jump off

00:30:25.790 --> 00:30:26.590
the balcony?

00:30:29.110 --> 00:30:30.130
Last night...

00:30:30.400 --> 00:30:32.040
I got drunk too.

00:30:32.590 --> 00:30:33.640
All I can recall

00:30:34.640 --> 00:30:35.400
is that he...

00:30:36.590 --> 00:30:39.390
he was standing in the balcony,
looking at the sky.

00:30:55.440 --> 00:30:57.100
All of a sudden, he jumped off.

00:31:09.900 --> 00:31:12.100
Did you know Li Jun was using LSD stamps?

00:31:15.270 --> 00:31:16.230
I knew.

00:31:18.640 --> 00:31:19.100
But I...

00:31:19.590 --> 00:31:23.250
But I didn't know he'd jump from heights
after using those stamps.

00:31:23.590 --> 00:31:24.450
Do you use them?

00:31:26.400 --> 00:31:27.030
No.

00:31:28.310 --> 00:31:30.170
I stay clear of that sort of stuff.

00:31:33.270 --> 00:31:35.800
How long had Li Jun been using stamps?

00:31:37.400 --> 00:31:38.070
Since...

00:31:39.370 --> 00:31:40.570
Since this month.

00:31:44.720 --> 00:31:45.440
Well,

00:31:45.590 --> 00:31:46.590
besides LSD stamps,

00:31:46.590 --> 00:31:48.320
did he use other types of drugs?

00:31:50.160 --> 00:31:51.030
No.

00:31:51.640 --> 00:31:52.660
I'm not sure.

00:31:57.640 --> 00:31:58.290
Where did he

00:31:58.290 --> 00:31:59.690
get the stamps?

00:32:03.310 --> 00:32:04.350
I think...

00:32:05.270 --> 00:32:06.840
he got them from a friend.

00:32:08.960 --> 00:32:09.790
A friend?

00:32:09.790 --> 00:32:10.480
What friend?

00:32:10.480 --> 00:32:12.010
Who? What's his or her name?

00:32:13.500 --> 00:32:14.830
A man named Zhe.

00:32:15.070 --> 00:32:16.130
How do you spell it?

00:32:16.270 --> 00:32:17.310
Z-H-E, Zhe.

00:32:18.310 --> 00:32:19.870
Zhe often gave him stamps.

00:32:21.960 --> 00:32:23.270
Apart from Zhe,

00:32:23.270 --> 00:32:25.400
did anyone else supply him with drugs?

00:32:28.920 --> 00:32:29.720
I don't know.

00:32:31.440 --> 00:32:32.640
I really don't know.

00:32:36.270 --> 00:32:37.750
I dared not ask him,

00:32:39.270 --> 00:32:41.000
or intervene with this matter.

00:32:43.640 --> 00:32:44.110
I...

00:32:44.640 --> 00:32:45.300
I feared...

00:32:47.000 --> 00:32:47.940
I feared him.

00:32:53.640 --> 00:32:54.700
Why?

00:32:58.110 --> 00:33:00.190
I feared that he'd abuse me.

00:33:06.720 --> 00:33:07.480
Look.

00:33:08.200 --> 00:33:10.330
These all resulted from his beatings.

00:33:14.390 --> 00:33:15.590
Put your coat back on.

00:33:23.200 --> 00:33:24.720
Did you hate Li Jun?

00:33:29.590 --> 00:33:30.960
You want me to tell the truth?

00:33:30.960 --> 00:33:31.920
Of course.

00:33:35.590 --> 00:33:36.000
I...

00:33:36.480 --> 00:33:37.740
I hated him sometimes.

00:33:39.270 --> 00:33:40.000
But...

00:33:40.640 --> 00:33:43.570
he actually treated me quite well
in most of the time.

00:33:44.270 --> 00:33:46.270
Only when he used those stamps

00:33:47.270 --> 00:33:49.400
would he turn into a different person.

00:33:58.270 --> 00:33:59.720
Let me comb through the story

00:33:59.720 --> 00:34:00.650
you just told us.

00:34:01.790 --> 00:34:04.240
That night, Li Jun used LSD stamps.

00:34:05.110 --> 00:34:06.240
Then, he beat you up.

00:34:06.310 --> 00:34:07.330
Afterwards,

00:34:07.790 --> 00:34:09.960
he jumped off the balcony
right before your eyes

00:34:09.960 --> 00:34:11.110
and died, right?

00:34:13.960 --> 00:34:15.219
You're suspecting me,

00:34:16.510 --> 00:34:17.170
aren't you?

00:34:18.800 --> 00:34:20.110
You think I killed him?

00:34:21.800 --> 00:34:23.070
I'm also a victim.

00:34:24.960 --> 00:34:26.030
What have I done wrong

00:34:26.030 --> 00:34:28.030
to deserve such treatment from you?

00:34:29.150 --> 00:34:31.030
All I did was date him.

00:34:31.030 --> 00:34:33.230
Why do you have to question me like this?

00:34:33.320 --> 00:34:34.550
I'm wallowing in grief.

00:34:34.550 --> 00:34:35.590
Alright.

00:34:36.110 --> 00:34:36.920
I'm sorry.

00:34:37.280 --> 00:34:38.630
But this is the standard procedure.

00:34:38.630 --> 00:34:40.090
I hope you can understand.

00:34:40.550 --> 00:34:41.710
Let's leave it at that for now.

00:34:41.710 --> 00:34:41.960
Zhi'an,

00:34:41.960 --> 00:34:43.150
take her for a drug test

00:34:43.150 --> 00:34:43.960
and have her injuries examined.

00:34:43.960 --> 00:34:44.480
Okay.

00:34:45.510 --> 00:34:46.190
Captain Luo,

00:34:46.190 --> 00:34:47.590
Do you find Mai Jiamin suspicious?

00:34:47.590 --> 00:34:48.710
What's your opinion?

00:34:48.710 --> 00:34:50.320
She strikes me as a foolish girl,

00:34:50.320 --> 00:34:52.150
for not breaking up with an abuser.

00:34:52.150 --> 00:34:54.210
Nothing else seems suspicious to me.

00:34:54.760 --> 00:34:55.920
But I always have a feeling

00:34:55.920 --> 00:34:57.110
that she was trying too hard

00:34:57.110 --> 00:34:58.520
to present herself as a victim.

00:34:58.520 --> 00:34:59.590
Captain Luo,

00:34:59.590 --> 00:35:00.590
as police officers,

00:35:00.590 --> 00:35:01.880
we can't base our judgements
on our feelings only.

00:35:01.880 --> 00:35:03.670
Evidence has to be taken into account.

00:35:03.670 --> 00:35:04.150
Kiddo,

00:35:04.150 --> 00:35:05.110
you can speak standard Mandarin.

00:35:05.110 --> 00:35:06.190
Why do you have to imitate me?

00:35:06.190 --> 00:35:08.110
It's not true. I'm not imitating you.

00:35:08.110 --> 00:35:09.660
I think
Yipeng has been a bad influence on you.

00:35:09.660 --> 00:35:10.390
Captain Luo,

00:35:10.510 --> 00:35:11.800
the drug test results are in.

00:35:11.800 --> 00:35:13.150
There is alcohol in Mai Jiamin's system.

00:35:13.150 --> 00:35:14.810
No traces of drugs were found.

00:35:15.150 --> 00:35:16.190
This proves

00:35:16.190 --> 00:35:18.280
Mai Jiamin is clean.

00:35:19.920 --> 00:35:22.180
Has Li Jun's autopsy report come out yet?

00:35:22.400 --> 00:35:24.110
The preliminary finding
is that he overdosed

00:35:24.110 --> 00:35:25.110
and died in a fall.

00:35:25.110 --> 00:35:27.480
But there won't be final results
until two days later.

00:35:27.480 --> 00:35:28.630
Send them over once they're in.

00:35:28.630 --> 00:35:28.960
Okay.

00:35:29.920 --> 00:35:31.150
Alright. Get back to your work.

00:35:31.150 --> 00:35:31.710
Got it.

00:36:16.280 --> 00:36:18.340
Hello. Please sign for your package.

00:36:36.960 --> 00:36:38.020
You made your pick?

00:36:45.000 --> 00:36:45.660
Sixty yuan.

00:36:48.670 --> 00:36:49.190
Okay.

00:36:51.030 --> 00:36:51.760
Here you are.

00:37:00.580 --> 00:37:04.230
[Baiye Music Store]

00:37:18.760 --> 00:37:20.620
[A White Night]

00:37:49.900 --> 00:37:51.040
How do you know

00:37:51.180 --> 00:37:52.510
that girl is into drugs?

00:37:56.320 --> 00:37:57.680
She used to be in a band.

00:37:57.960 --> 00:37:58.730
I know that.

00:38:01.960 --> 00:38:02.690
Good for you.

00:38:05.510 --> 00:38:06.030
Little did I realize

00:38:06.030 --> 00:38:07.830
you used to be the artistic type.

00:38:09.880 --> 00:38:12.580
[Welcome]
[Open]

00:38:58.230 --> 00:38:59.290
What are you doing?

00:39:06.960 --> 00:39:08.360
Did you use those stamps?

00:39:09.670 --> 00:39:11.870
You just can't shake off that bad habit!

00:39:12.280 --> 00:39:12.980
Come on.

00:39:13.320 --> 00:39:13.880
Come with me.

00:39:13.880 --> 00:39:14.800
Get out of the room.

00:39:14.800 --> 00:39:16.030
Let your daughter see
what a mess you are.

00:39:16.030 --> 00:39:17.030
Come on. Move it!

00:39:18.920 --> 00:39:19.780
Move it!

00:39:21.800 --> 00:39:22.780
I'm begging you.

00:39:23.020 --> 00:39:24.880
Don't let Cotton know about this.

00:39:24.990 --> 00:39:26.470
Keep it secret from her.

00:39:26.800 --> 00:39:27.540
Please.

00:39:27.760 --> 00:39:28.890
Answer my question.

00:39:29.150 --> 00:39:30.880
Where did you get those stamps?

00:39:31.440 --> 00:39:32.210
Where?

00:39:32.800 --> 00:39:35.030
From a vinyl someone returned.

00:39:36.960 --> 00:39:37.790
Which vinyl?

00:39:39.800 --> 00:39:40.680
I don't know.

00:39:42.280 --> 00:39:43.310
I don't know.

00:39:43.800 --> 00:39:45.080
I really don't know.

00:39:45.110 --> 00:39:46.880
Look at me! Look me in the eyes!

00:39:48.320 --> 00:39:49.250
If you don't want

00:39:49.550 --> 00:39:50.630
your daughter to see

00:39:50.630 --> 00:39:51.630
what a wreck you're now,

00:39:51.630 --> 00:39:52.190
you'd better behave.

00:39:52.190 --> 00:39:52.990
Do you hear me?

00:39:53.320 --> 00:39:54.690
If you dare to touch that stuff again—

00:39:54.690 --> 00:39:55.500
listen up—

00:39:55.550 --> 00:39:56.550
I'll kick you out!

00:39:56.710 --> 00:39:57.300
Out!

00:40:00.470 --> 00:40:04.670
[Police Line]

00:40:09.190 --> 00:40:11.140
[Police Line]

00:40:24.230 --> 00:40:28.090
[A White Night]

00:40:28.090 --> 00:40:29.070
Zhan Cui...

00:40:33.190 --> 00:40:34.000
Ms. Lin!

00:40:44.800 --> 00:40:45.440
I found it.

00:40:50.480 --> 00:40:51.210
What's this?

00:40:51.260 --> 00:40:51.920
[A White Night]

00:40:51.920 --> 00:40:52.970
I know her.

00:40:53.480 --> 00:40:54.210
You know her?

00:40:55.970 --> 00:40:59.370
[Baiye Music Store]

00:41:20.850 --> 00:41:28.100
[A White Night]

00:41:35.910 --> 00:41:39.160
♪ Loneliness and despair
flood in like tides ♪

00:41:39.920 --> 00:41:42.910
♪ I long to be seen and loved,
as I hate to feel lonesome again ♪

00:41:43.570 --> 00:41:45.710
♪ Fear occupies my heart,
pushing me into a dead end ♪

00:41:45.710 --> 00:41:46.650
Excuse me.

00:41:47.270 --> 00:41:47.510
♪ Vanity sticks with me;
With desires filled, I still feel hollow ♪

00:41:47.510 --> 00:41:48.710
We're about to close.

00:41:48.960 --> 00:41:49.890
This early?

00:41:50.630 --> 00:41:52.710
We're taking an inventory this afternoon.

00:41:52.710 --> 00:41:54.040
Are you the store owner?

00:41:54.320 --> 00:41:54.970
No.

00:41:55.960 --> 00:41:58.190
It's really hard to buy vinyls nowadays,

00:41:58.190 --> 00:42:00.520
with all sorts of music available online.

00:42:01.590 --> 00:42:03.240
I have eclectic tastes in music.

00:42:03.240 --> 00:42:04.440
I'll take two vinyls.

00:42:05.590 --> 00:42:07.120
The one labelled "Mozart."

00:42:07.630 --> 00:42:08.280
Mozart.

00:42:11.030 --> 00:42:12.850
As for the other one...

00:42:13.350 --> 00:42:14.400
That album of Queen.

00:42:14.400 --> 00:42:15.590
I love that band.

00:42:16.960 --> 00:42:17.890
You have great taste.

00:42:17.890 --> 00:42:18.510
Thanks.

00:42:20.480 --> 00:42:22.920
This store mainly sells instrument now,
huh?

00:42:22.920 --> 00:42:24.900
Not many buyers of vinyls, right?

00:42:25.400 --> 00:42:26.130
Eighty yuan.

00:42:26.280 --> 00:42:26.960
Okay.

00:42:26.960 --> 00:42:27.730
Eighty...

00:42:30.450 --> 00:42:31.440
Here's a 50.

00:42:31.960 --> 00:42:33.260
Twenty.

00:42:38.630 --> 00:42:39.630
Make it 70.

00:42:39.630 --> 00:42:40.550
Give me a discount, will you?

00:42:40.550 --> 00:42:41.750
I'll come back again.

00:42:41.880 --> 00:42:42.400
Fine.

00:42:43.880 --> 00:42:44.410
Besides,

00:42:44.960 --> 00:42:46.560
can you do me a favor?

00:42:47.110 --> 00:42:47.800
Look.

00:42:48.710 --> 00:42:50.110
This is my guitar.

00:42:50.550 --> 00:42:52.190
It's broken. Can you fix it?

00:42:52.670 --> 00:42:53.570
Seems serious.

00:42:56.030 --> 00:42:57.320
Bring it to me next time.

00:42:57.320 --> 00:42:58.600
Great. Thank you.

00:43:04.960 --> 00:43:06.400
This woman looks a lot like you.

00:43:06.400 --> 00:43:07.460
Is it you?

00:43:07.880 --> 00:43:08.550
No.

00:43:08.550 --> 00:43:10.210
What a striking resemblance.

00:43:10.800 --> 00:43:11.460
It's not me.

00:43:13.060 --> 00:43:14.310
You two look really alike.

00:43:14.310 --> 00:43:15.090
I'm leaving then.

00:43:15.090 --> 00:43:15.510
[Welcome]
[Open]

00:43:15.510 --> 00:43:16.790
See you next time.

00:43:16.880 --> 00:43:17.770
Take care.

00:43:31.280 --> 00:43:35.220
[Notice]
[Resting]

00:43:35.220 --> 00:43:37.380
[Baiye Music Store]

00:44:15.260 --> 00:44:16.760
Here's your Four Fruits Sweet Soup.

00:44:16.760 --> 00:44:17.360
Thank you.

00:44:23.970 --> 00:44:25.870
[Baiye Music Store]

00:44:30.280 --> 00:44:31.190
Officer Ruan.

00:44:31.510 --> 00:44:32.290
There you are.